0.04  Sun Jul 21 00:00:00 2002
	- fixed another minor bug

0.05  Sun Nov 21 00:00:00 2004
	- added support for output to a scalar

0.06  Mon Apr 18 00:00:00 2005
        - added UTF-8 support

0.07  Sun May 15 00:00:00 2005
        - fixed some major bugs with UTF-8 support
        - added better support for multiple detail sections
	- added support for input from a scalar
	- added two escape encoding types
	- added the common parameters feature
